<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>FlyBuddy – AI Flight Companion</title>

<meta name="description"
      content="FlyBuddy is an AI-powered iOS flight companion for smarter travel, airport navigation, real-time flight tracking and stress-free flying with Bob.">

<meta name="keywords"
      content="FlyBuddy, flight tracker, airport navigation, AI travel app, iOS flight app, flight companion, travel assistant, airport app">

<meta name="author" content="JSPixelcraft">

<style>

* {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    background: #0b0f19;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 60px 24px;
}

.logo {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto 24px auto;

    width: 220px;
    max-width: 80%;
    border-radius: 28px;

    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
}

.hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 0 80px;
}

.badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    background: rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.25);
    color: #7dd3fc;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 72px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
}

.hero p {
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #b8c1d1;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: auto;
}

.hero-buttons {
    margin-top: 40px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.btn {
    padding: 16px 28px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.25s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.btn-primary {
    background: #7dd3fc;
    color: #0b0f19;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    color: white;
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}

.section {
    margin-top: 90px;
}

.section-title {
    font-size: 42px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    text-align: center;
}

.section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: #b8c1d1;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: auto auto 50px;
}

.grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
}

.card {
    background: #151b2c;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 30px;
    transition: 0.25s ease;
}

.card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
}

.card h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 24px;
}

.card p {
    color: #b8c1d1;
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.premium {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2940, #111827);
}

.showcase {
    margin-top: 80px;

    background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(125,211,252,0.08),
        rgba(255,255,255,0.02)
    );

    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 32px;

    padding: 60px 40px;

    text-align: center;
}

.showcase h2 {
    font-size: 42px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.showcase p {
    color: #b8c1d1;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: auto;
}

.footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 120px;
    color: #7f8aa3;
    font-size: 15px;
}

.highlight {
    color: #7dd3fc;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
    }

    .hero p {
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: 32px;
    }

    .logo {
        width: 170px;
    }

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="hero">

        <img src="logofly.png" class="logo">

        <div class="badge">
             AI-Powered Flight Companion
        </div>

        <h1>
            FlyBuddy
        </h1>

        <p>
            Your smart AI-powered travel companion for real-time flight tracking,
            airport navigation and modern travel chaos.

            <span class="highlight">
                Built for iPhone travelers who want less stress and smarter flying.
            </span>
        </p>

        <div class="hero-buttons">

            <a class="btn btn-primary"
               href="https://apps.apple.com/">
               Get it now
            </a>


        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="section" id="features">

        <h2 class="section-title">
            Everything for modern travel
        </h2>

        <p class="section-subtitle">
            Track flights in real time, navigate airports faster
            and get intelligent travel assistance exactly when you need it.
        </p>

        <div class="grid">

            <div class="card">

                <h2>✈️ Real-Time Flight Tracking</h2>

                <p>
                    Track departures, arrivals, delays, gate changes
                    and live flight timelines in real time.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h2>🧭 Smart Airport Navigation</h2>

                <p>
                    Navigate terminals, gates and airport locations
                    faster with intelligent travel tools.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h2>🤖 Meet Bob</h2>

                <p>
                    Your slightly chaotic AI travel companion helps guide you
                    through stressful travel situations with humor and alerts.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h2>📍 Context-Aware Travel</h2>

                <p>
                    FlyBuddy adapts to your current journey,
                    airport and travel situation automatically.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h2>🛫 Flight Timeline</h2>

                <p>
                    Stay ahead of delays, boarding windows
                    and important airport events.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card premium">

                <h2>🌙 FlyBuddy Premium</h2>

                <p>
                    Unlock smarter AI interactions,
                    advanced travel features and future premium tools.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="showcase">

        <h2>
            Designed for real travelers
        </h2>

        <p>
            FlyBuddy helps travelers survive airport chaos,
            stressful delays and modern flying with
            intelligent travel assistance and personality.
        </p>

    </div>


    <div class="section">

        <h2 class="section-title">
            Why FlyBuddy?
        </h2>

        <p class="section-subtitle">
            Modern iOS design combined with intelligent travel tools
            for smoother journeys.
        </p>

        <div class="grid">

            <div class="card">

                <h2>⚡ Fast & Simple</h2>

                <p>
                    Open the app and instantly access
                    the information you actually need.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h2>📡 Smart Live Updates</h2>

                <p>
                    Stay informed about delays,
                    gate changes and important travel events.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h2>📱 Built for iPhone</h2>

                <p>
                    Designed specifically for iOS with smooth interactions,
                    modern visuals and fast performance.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="footer">
        © 2026 FlyBuddy — Travel smarter. Less stress. More flying.
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
